## Good to Know

- Full commercial kitchen and catering available through Hopewell Hall
- Peaceful lakeside setting in Butler, Ohio
- We do not host rentals for family gatherings, parties, or weddings
- **Rentals not available June & July** (summer camp season)
- Contact us: **(567) 772-4322** or **info@otyokwah.org**
- Located at 3380 Tugend Rd, Butler, OH 44822

